<!DOCTYPE html><html class=""><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>Blot</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/blot.css?1520793197215"></head><body class="sans-serif f5 lh-copy"><div class="nav fixed"><div class="center mw8 ph4"><a class="db fl w-left selected" href="/">Blot is a blogging platform</a><div><a class="db fl ph4 ml-4" href="/sign-up">Sign up</a> <a class="db fl ph4" href="/about">About</a> <a class="db fl ph4" href="/updates">Updates</a> <a class="db fl ph4" href="/contact">Contact</a> <a class="db fr ph4 mr-4" href="/log-in">Log in</a><div class="cf"></div></div></div></div><div class="wrapper"><div class="center mw8 ph4" style="padding-top:160px"><div class="fl sidebar fixed"><ul><a href="/" class="selected">Introduction</a></ul><ul><a href="/help" class="">How to use Blot</a></ul><ul><a href="/configuring" class="">Configuring your blog</a></ul><ul><a href="/account" class="">Account and billing</a></ul></div><div class="w-right-offset"><p class="mt0 measure">Blot is a blogging platform with no interface. It creates a special folder in your Dropbox and automatically publishes files you put inside. The point of all this&hairsp;—&hairsp;the reason Blot exists&hairsp;—&hairsp;is so you can use your favorite tools to create whatever you publish.</p><p class="measure mb0">Blot automatically creates blog posts from&nbsp;<nobr><icon class="md"></icon>Text and Markdown</nobr>,&nbsp;<nobr style="margin-left:-3px"><icon class="txt"></icon>&nbsp;Word Documents</nobr>,&nbsp;<nobr><icon class="img"></icon>&nbsp;Images</nobr>,<nobr><icon class="webloc"></icon>&nbsp;Bookmarks</nobr>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<nobr><icon class="html"></icon>&nbsp;HTML</nobr>. Just put the files in your blog’s folder and <a id="other_play" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_k2NQNj9-LE">Blot does the rest</a>.</p><div id="background" class="bg"><a id="closer" href="/" class=""><div class="mw8 center ph4 tr" style="line-height:80px"><span class=""><svg style="width:0.65rem;margin-right: 0.65rem" viewbox="0 0 50 50"><path d="M50 5l-5-5-20 20L5 0 0 5l20 20L0 45l5 5 20-20 20 20 5-5-20-20z"></path></svg>Close</span></div></a><div class="mw8 center v-mid" style="margin-top:5rem"><div class="ph4"><div id="thumb"><iframe id="video" class="" src="" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></div></div><div style="margin-top:5rem" class="bg"><div id="thumb"><a id="play" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_k2NQNj9-LE" target="_blank" class="mw8 center thumb pv5 db"><div class="buts"><img src="/images/play.png" width="17"></div><div class="measure" style=""><div style="width:58%;float:right"><window class="folder"><toolbar><dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots><icon class="dropbox"></icon>&nbsp;Your blog</toolbar><sorter>Name<icon class="chevron"></icon></sorter><contents><item class=""><icon class="folder"></icon>Drafts</item><item class=""><icon class="folder"></icon>Pages</item><item class="open"><icon class="folder"></icon>Posts</item><item class="nested-1"><icon class="file webloc"></icon>Bookmark.webloc</item><item class="nested-1"><icon class="file docx"></icon>Document.docx</item><item class="nested-1"><icon class="file img"></icon>Image.jpg</item><item class="nested-1"><icon class="file md"></icon>Markdown.md</item><item class="nested-1"><icon class="file txt"></icon>Text.txt</item><item class="nested-1"><icon class="file html"></icon>Webpage.html</item><item class="">&nbsp;</item><item class="">&nbsp;</item><item class="">&nbsp;</item></contents><border class="left"></border><border class="right"></border><border class="top"></border><border class="bottom"></border><corner class="top left"></corner><corner class="top right"></corner><corner class="bottom left"></corner><corner class="bottom right"></corner></window></div></div></a></div></div><p class="measure" style="margin-top:5rem">Blot comes with <a href="/configuring">seven templates</a>. They’re easy to customize, lightweight and designed to fit both small and large screens. You can also <a href="/developers">develop your own template</a> from scratch.</p><p class="measure">Here’s a handful of the websites hosted on Blot:</p><br><ul class="gallery large"><a href="https://www.matthewbattles.org/" target="_blank">matthewbattles.org<span class="new">New</span><dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://hannautkin.com/" target="_blank">hannautkin.com<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://juicenews.com/" target="_blank">juicenews.com<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://ylukem.com" target="_blank">ylukem.com<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://www.alexgibson.nyc/" target="_blank">alexgibson.nyc<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://www.theliminal.co/" target="_blank">theliminal.co<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://john.pavlusoffice.com/" target="_blank">johnpavlus.com<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://kiefer.design/" target="_blank">kiefer.design<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://www.2080.co/" target="_blank">2080.co<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://www.kristianhjelle.com" target="_blank">kristianhjelle.com<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a> <a href="https://mrfris.by/" target="_blank">mrfris.by<dots><dot></dot><dot></dot><dot></dot></dots></a></ul><div class="cf"></div><p style="margin-top:2.5rem" class="measure mb0">A blog costs <a href="/sign-up">$20 per year</a>. The annual fee pays for the servers which host your blog. It also covers the cost of providing support. Most importantly, it encourages Blot to operate in your best interests, as opposed to those of an advertiser or investor.</p></div></div><div class="cf"></div><div class="spacer cf half"></div><div class="push"></div></div><a href=